---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Situated Design Practice · Madlen von Wulffen"
  description="Four postcards written to practitioners met during the Situated Design Practices course."
>
  <div class="proj-layout">

    <div class="col-images">
      <figure>
        <img src={`${base}images/postcard%201.jpg`} alt="Postcard 1" />
        <figcaption>Postcard 1.</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure>
        <img src={`${base}images/postcard%202.jpg`} alt="Postcard 2" />
        <figcaption>Postcard 2.</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure>
        <img src={`${base}images/postcard%203.jpg`} alt="Postcard 3" />
        <figcaption>Postcard 3.</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure>
        <img src={`${base}images/postcard%204.jpg`} alt="Postcard 4" />
        <figcaption>Postcard 4.</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="col-text">
      <div class="text-inner">
        <div class="proj-category">Design Practice · 2026</div>
        <h1>Situated Design Practice</h1>
        <p class="lede">Four postcards written to practitioners met during the Situated Design Practices course — reflecting on their stories and my own creative practice.</p>

        <h2>Four Letters on Practice</h2>
        <p>I love letters. Especially love letters. I am writing at least one letter or postcard every week to my beloved grandmother, my best friend or my godchild, Camilla.</p>
        <p>For this, I took the advantage of pursuing my letter writing and created four postcards to the people I was able to meet and listen to during the course "Situated Design Practices" — to reflect on their stories and my own creative practice.</p>

        <div class="meta-table">
          <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Time</span><span class="meta-val">Feb 17 – 20, 2026</span></div>
          <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Context</span><span class="meta-val">Situated Design Practices</span></div>
          <div class="meta-row"><span class="meta-key">Outcome</span><span class="meta-val">4 Postcards</span></div>
        </div>

        <a class="back-link" href={`${base}projects`}>← Back to Projects</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .proj-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    height: calc(100vh - 56px);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .col-images {
    height: 100%;
    overflow-y: scroll;
    border-right: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0;
  }
  figure {
    margin: 0;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0;
  }
  figure img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }
  figcaption {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem 1rem;
    border-top: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0;
  }
  .col-text {
    height: 100%;
    overflow-y: scroll;
  }
  .text-inner {
    padding: 3rem 2.2rem 4rem;
  }
  .proj-category {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
    text-transform: none;
  }
  .lede {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0;
    padding-bottom: 1.4rem;
  }
  .col-text p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #2a2a2a;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 2rem 0 0.8rem;
  }
  .meta-table {
    margin-top: 2.4rem;
    border-top: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0;
    padding-top: 1.4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.7rem;
  }
  .meta-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }
  .meta-key {
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding-top: 0.15rem;
  }
  .meta-val {
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .meta-val a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 2.4rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  :global(body:has(.proj-layout) footer) { display: none; }
  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .proj-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; height: auto; overflow: visible; }
    .col-images, .col-text { height: auto; overflow-y: visible; }
    .col-images { border-right: none; border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0; }
  }
</style>
